      "id": "PopularPost348591",
      "post_content": "I like seeing these sacrifice effects spread out to Red as well as Black and Artifact.   \n  \nProbably nothing will ever top [Ashnod's Altar](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ashnod's Altar) and [Altar of Dementia](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Altar of Dementia) for both flavor and power, but it's the thought that counts. :)",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
