    {
      "id": "PopularPost349782",
      "post_content": "in comparison, [Barrage of Expendables](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Barrage of Expendables) is a ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol)-cost enchantment that only costs ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) to activate it. The only difference is dealing 1 damage versus 2. I mean, dealing 2 damage at the cost of one sac'ed creature is better than 1, but all of these additional costs add up. That being said, Barrage isn't as good as Goblin Bombardment.   \n  \nRegardless, the art is beyond awesome and gruesome. You don't see something as visceral as this every day.",
      "posted_by": "Ferlord",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost349782\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">in comparison, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Barrage of Expendables\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Barrage of Expendables\">Barrage of Expendables</a> is a <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/>-cost enchantment that only costs <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> to activate it. The only difference is dealing 1 damage versus 2. I mean, dealing 2 damage at the cost of one sac'ed creature is better than 1, but all of these additional costs add up. That being said, Barrage isn't as good as Goblin Bombardment. <br/><br/>Regardless, the art is beyond awesome and gruesome. You don't see something as visceral as this every day.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '349782'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy54405\">Ferlord</span>\r\n                                (11/4/2013 11:50:54 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>